      About this item

      • [H.265+ 8CH 5MP Lite HD-TVI DVR] With our advanced H.265+ 8CH 5MP Lite HD-TVI DVR, you can enjoy high-quality video with low bit-rate due to the doubled data compression ratio provided by the H.265 technology. This DVR maximizes storage space, ensuring ultra-long recording without compromising video quality. Perfect for home security camera systems. Note: This system does not include a hard drive. If you need to record, you will need to purchase an additional hard drive
      • [Accurate Person and Vehicle Detection] With AI-powered detection system that accurately identifies and alerts you to any person or vehicle. Stay connected with our free app for live view and playback on your smart devices from anywhere, anytime
      • [IP66 Weatherproof & 80ft Night Vision] Designed with IP66 weatherproof camera housing, our cameras can be installed in any indoor or outdoor location. The high-quality ABS materials effectively prevent rust, ensuring durability and long-lasting performance. In addition, the built-in 24pcs IR LEDs provide up to 80ft night vision in total darkness and 130ft night vision in ambient light, ensuring clear and sharp images day or night.
      • [Expandable camera system] Our expandable camera system offers flexibility with an 8-channel 4-in-1 DVR that supports analog HD-TVI CVI AHD cameras. Easily extend your surveillance coverage by adding up to 4 additional 720P or 1080P bullet or dome cameras to your system.
      • [No Include Hard Drive] Please note that this system is sold without a hard drive. However, it is easy to assemble a 3.5 inch SATA 500GB to 2TB hard drive for your recording needs. The DVR need to work with a hard drive to record(not included). If you have product problems, please contact us anytime.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      • BigDek68
        5.0 out of 5 stars Great VFM kit.
        Reviewed in Canada on May 16, 2017
        Size: Wired-4CamVerified Purchase
        great all round system. price point was a little off putting at first, but bit the bullet and took the plunge. Using eight cameras as a home CCTV system. domed shaped camera housing blends quite nicely with the exterior of my home.

        PROS - easy to install and set up, system menu easy to follow, DVR is discreet and wouldn't look out of place under your TV next to your TV cable /sat boxes

        CONS - care and attention is required when positioning cameras. Held in place by small rubber grommets which are easily dislodged. If displaced after the camera has been installed, the camera itself becomes 'floppy' and you'll need to hold it place with tape (yuk) or gunning some silicon sealant.

        I had 3 cameras go 'floppy' on me and were replaced quickly, efficiently and free by Zosi. Very impressive customer service.

        The app which allows you to connect remotely to your system can be a little awkward. I consider myself to be extremely technologically proficient, however, I still required assistance with setting up the app on my iPhone.

        Would highly recommend this unit for personal and small business usage.

        The fact that you need to purchase your own hard drive is a bonus too, as you are able to select a memory size to suit your needs and price bracket rather than pay over the odds for a drive you can pick up for considerably less. I went with a 1Tb Western Digital drive for approx C$70.00 from amazon.ca

        edit (have put this unit up to 5 stars.) ;

        having owned this system for a few weeks I can honestly say that it is performing beyond expectations. Zosi customer service is second to none, and what price for peace of mind when away from home. Night operation and clarity is crystal clear, reviewing video feeds from my iPhone is very easy, as is accessing the recorded video. take your time to learn the full functionality of the DVR system and you will not be disappointed.
